phrases: Thank you for your help, Kanou-kun.
He helped me carry the papers.
When did you two get so close?
I thought that I might be able to overcome my aversion towards girls if I spent time with Yukimura-senpai.
I said I am not a girl.
You are just saying that, are not you?
Why can I hear what they are thinking?
I will become a man among men!
I will go get the other documents, too.
No, I am doing it by myself.
Fine, I will train to become manly then.
I will become manly enough to totally surprise you.
He found himself a good guardian.
Oh yeah, I owe him one.
You want to pay me back?
First you saved me when a stalker was after me, and then during the sports festival,
and even when I had trouble with Kanou, too.
I do not like being so indebted to you.
Well, then be my maid for a day.
Could you think of something else?
Do you seriously want me to be your maid for a day?
I never thought you were that messed up.
It actually worries me that that is the only thing you want.
You are actually ready for me to do naughty things to you?
Time to go to your job, Prez.
How does that idiot want this to end?!
What is this important thing it is referring to?!
I only made one card that gives horrible luck.
In a way, he is actually amazingly lucky.
Do not worry, we got great luck.
It is just a homemade fortune cookie.
Then you take one, too, Misa-chan.
If you get the same result, it will probably make him happy.
If you owe someone a favor, make sure you pay them back.
We are closing for the day.
Who is the owner of this place?
Yes, I am the manager here.
I am sorry about this sudden proposal.
We would like to buy this shop.
I am a member of the Maki Dining Group.
You do not know them, Aoi-chan?
They are the biggest player in the food service industry,
running everything from major family restaurants to high class restaurants.
It is an honor that you are so familiar with my father's company.
He is the son of the CEO?
You see, we plan on opening a new store.
When we thought of the target customers, we realized that this location would be the best.
So I brought up the project proposal several times.
To the owner of this building.
You plan on buying the entire building?
Unfortunately, though, he would not assent.
I am protecting this place until the day I die.
I cannot trouble any of the tenants.
That is why I am visiting every tenant, explaining the situation.
Basically you are trying to get rid of Maid Latte, right?!
Go open your store somewhere else!
And this shop that we are going to start is-
I do not think a detailed explanation is necessary to those who work here.
That is why we would like to open our shop here.
If it is just a cafe, why are you going for the entire building?
Well, we plan on demolishing the building and building a western style mansion.
Rather than a cafe, it is closer to being a restaurant.
We plan on serving a full course dinner, too.
A slightly fancy butler cafe, I guess.
Butlers and waiters are not the same!
He is Miyabigaoka's proud vice president.
Miyabigaoka's Student Council President, Igarashi Tora.
As the vice president, he makes an excellent assistant.
You might say that he knows the joy of working for a master.
I believe that he can make a great shop, so I am supporting him as the president and as his friend.
If you are worried about his capability as a butler, how about you come to the footman audition held next weekend?
They are staff who work under the butler.
In order to hire skilled footmen, we will be holding a large scale interview.
It is still too early to recruit staff!
Nobody said they are selling this place!
Maki-kun, we will need to give them time to relax and think.
Here is the summary of the conditions and benefits related to this sale.
Please look over this and consider our proposal.
If you cannot agree to the listed price for terms such as mediating the reemployment of your staff and funding to relocate,
we are willing to negotiate on these points.
You should not be out in that, should you?
Is it because I am here?
You are great at acting, as always.
Dressed up in pretty interesting clothes, are not you?
Just so you know, I am only watching from the sideline, since it is the first shop Maki's organizing.
He seriously wants to be successful.
This place has been built on the work we and the Chief did together.
We have customers coming back because they like it here.
How could you take this place away from them, too...
You seem really into your job as a maid.
Once you graduate, do you plan on becoming a professional maid?
Then why do not you seriously spar with Maki?
Unless you surpass his determination, you will not get anywhere.
For instance, the audition that is being held next weekend.
It is a perfect chance to show how serious you are with greeting customers.
I have to pay back the humiliation he put me through, playing along with his perverted games.
I cannot forgive something like this.
I will do anything to get back at him.
Let me take that bag for you.
Nobody will know you are girls!
I am not sure if I should be happy or not.
I wrapped a cloth around my chest, wore a wig, and somehow managed to look like a guy.
There is nothing we could have done.
We had to have a pair of boys to meet the entry conditions.
Besides, you said you wanted to fight for the sake of Maid Latte, so it is natural that I take part in it.
If we make them realize that Maid Latte has a great staff, then maybe we can get out of this.
To be honest, I wanted to take part in it, but I have this rack that I just cannot hide.
Are you jealous of the great plains?
If I was not working at Maid Latte, I am sure they would not have made such a forceful buyout attempt.
Because of me, a place that is important to all of us could be gone.
Are not there way too many people here?
It is like a guy festival.
Look at that afro in the middle of the pack.
Did everyone come here just because they saw the flier?
If there is only a skill test and no written exam, we have to try it out, right?
It did not sound like a formal interview, either.
Come to the audition if you are interested, eh?
That is something that can only be done with the kind of trusted name the Maki Dining Group has.
I just realized the size of our competition.
Thank you for coming to this event.
We would like to start the audition now.
It is the vice president of Miyabigaoka, Maki Kanade!
The first thing we will have you do today is,
But what is the point of it?
The hill you came up while coming here is the course.
If you get to the bottom, you will find the turnaround point.
When you come back, please follow the usher to the gym, where we are.
I already do not have much confidence.
However, since this is an audition done by pairs,
the passing condition is for you to finish with your partner on your back.
This is going to be hot.
They have got to be kidding.
Please have your partner on your back at all times.
You may switch as many times as you like.
The first 50 to come back will move on.
Please assemble at the starting line.
Things like these are easy for me.
We cannot fight against someone that holds such a grand audition.
Besides, if they find out that you are girls-
It is not like you to give up before trying, Chief.
Could you just let me be selfish and do it?
I will make sure Misa-chan does not get hurt.
The fire does not go out once it is been lit, does it?
They make me feel they will accomplish something.
Despite what I said back there, it is me who is making the Chief look like that.
It is because Miyabigaoka's president has a grudge against me that Maid Latte is...
This should be easy for Misa-chan.
It is hard to move around in a suit, but I think we can pass this stage easily.
Let us work through this together, Misa-chan!
You should be invincible with us to support you!
Stamina's the only thing Shiroyan has-
There are lots of different kinds of people taking part in this, are not there?
Looks like there are fast people.
Good luck to you, too, Subaru.
Stop sexually harassing me in the public.
Touching a guy's chest is not sexual harassment.
Even if it is not, please stop.
Let me do some of the work next time, too.
How do you know I cannot before we even try it?
Could you lend me those fake glasses of yours?
Those who passed the first stage, please enter the gym.
We will now proceed to the next stage.
You can play baseball in here.
I can hardly tell that it is them standing there.
Are they interested in a job like this?
If they find out who I am now, it will get ugly.
Good work with the first assignment.
Many of you were probably surprised by the unique task you were given.
We wanted to see how serious you are.
I will be frank with you.
Working as a footman is very rigorous.
And because it is rigorous, you need the ability to help your colleague.
That is why this is a pair audition.
We will use it to see how well you can cooperate and complete your tasks.
The judges will be butlers, including myself and the student council president of Miyabigaoka Academy that lent us the campus,
There you are, you perverted tyrant.
I will make it all the way to the end.
We will now move on to the next assignment.
That concludes the 1st phase of the audition, which tested your stamina.
Being a footman requires this much strength?
Before we move on to the 2nd phase, we would like you to get changed.
We will provide you with a tailcoat now, and you have one minute.
You must be quick at anything.
The changing room for the two of you will get taken away a minute later, so please watch out.
Misaki-kun's always fast, so she is probably fine, but Subaru-kun's...
I knew she would be out.
Then maybe those masked guys are actually girls, too!
I cannot believe we are getting called out for this.
So much for all of our efforts.
Only males of high school age or older are allowed.
Excuse me, but please tell me your gender and age.
He is still in middle school?
That is why I was wearing a mask.
I will ask you two as well.
That automatically disqualifies the partner, so please leave together.
Perhaps the woman and the child made it this far because their partners were strong.
It would be a waste to lose a valuable human resource like this.
How about we have the remaining two form a new pair?
But of course, only if they are both qualified to be here.
Please let me confirm, just in case.
I can buy that from him, but I am not so sure about the one with glasses.
Yeah, the partner was a girl, after all.
It is as flat as a board.
So he was a guy, after all.
Yeah, it was easy to tell.
We will now move on to Phase 2.
Is that just how things went?
Or was it a set up?
I ended up pairing up with Usui.
How about you stare back at him?
He will find it more interesting.
Maybe you should take a deep breath.
Wow, it is Yukimura and Kanou.
It is not starting right now.
We were talking about next week.
